      <description/>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Jun 2025 20:30:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <content:encoded>&lt;b&gt;편집자주: 이 기사는 이혼 소송 과정에서 필요한 법률 지식을 제공할 목적으로 제작됐습니다. 기사 내용은 실제 사례를 각색했습니다. 기사 내 언급되는 이름과 지명 등이 실제와 같은 경우가 있더라도 이는 우연에 의한 것임을 밝힙니다.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;격주 토요일·일요일 연재.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img align="center" src="https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/chosun/UIUKBXCGAZEXPGBNPMVPX3M2SA.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img align="center" src="https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/chosun/NBVTAT2PV5DS5DJJIG2IV2IBQI.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img align="center" src="https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/chosun/SAHUZDGTA5FWJIHM22DOGTAALU.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img align="center" src="https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/chosun/DZLZEID2LZB7BFXP3UR3IPMP6A.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img align="center" src="https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/chosun/JNUW3F7PXVEJFB3ABHEZI4WTAA.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;[이별전쟁] 연애학개론②에서 계속&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&amp;lt;다른 회차 보기&amp;gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;잠수이별①&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;https://m.site.naver.com/1IjBe&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;잠수이별②&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;https://m.site.naver.com/1IjBo&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</content:encoded>
      <media:content url="https://www.chosun.com/resizer/v2/WM2R3RRXENHW7EKLK3J2H7HDKY.png?auth=4c8b1815d459a2c263106ae8c3a969a860c9e78b51852647eb3a9d1c43a040a0&amp;smart=true&amp;width=1800&amp;height=1012" type="image/png" height="1012" width="1800"/>
